{"tid":1131720,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【笑匠決戰】淥死誰手 同 唧黑頭 邊個爛gag好笑啲？","createTime":"2019-04-30T00:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T00:09:44.000Z","uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd756cc2a041f7613c140d2ad29cb432ecf4e60f","tid":1131720,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淥死誰手<br />\n<br />\n打邊爐無筷子，淥死誰手，哈哈哈哈哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唧黑頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nsXaJP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nsXaJP.png&h=c6f654e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"407a366c9259f7593cf86f9f41e9b7132fc14fdf","tid":1131720,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:08:40.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤和師弟楊天宇前晚出席代言戶日本健膚品牌UL．OS活動，席間兩人即場度胸肌，最後由43吋胸肌的阿澤鬥贏36吋的楊天宇，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>阿澤笑言：「我大過佢，不過佢長過我，話佢隻腳呀！」</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主持提及阿澤喜歡下廚，他<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即抵死說：「做廚房佬成日偷食，但用濕紙巾抹嘴就大步檻過。」</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當播出兩人的廣告片時，現場有人要求阿澤即場Rap，阿澤即謂：「本來有人9月開騷（指許志安紅館騷） ，如果我攞到個期，幾多錢我都畀。」引得全場爆笑！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提到見到身旁的師弟高大又靚仔會否好羨慕？阿澤笑謂：「咁又唔會，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我有嘅嘢佢又冇嘅，不過我啲長處都係收埋好啲。」</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問到他會否惹來不少飛來蜢？他直言：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我本身好唔受歡迎，男又好女又好</span></strong></span>，所以我從來都唔擔心呢啲問題，所以老婆一向都好放心，因為我生得醜，所以冇呢啲煩憂。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔得啦澤囝實在太好笑 我笑到好辛苦呀！<br />\n紅字為笑點👆👆👆<br />\n<br />\n巴打我留意左你好耐<br />\n你真係好幽默<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默既人 但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍<br />\n錯 應該係100倍先岩<br />\n估唔到我係呢個post竟然見識到你既威力<br />\n我真係笑到爆左肚 依家一路打字一路撿返d腸呀內臟呀腎呀<br />\n塞返落個肚到<br />\n你有冇諗過<del>未來幾個</del><strong>九</strong>月去紅館開棟篤笑?"},{"pid":"d894678f7142cecf31fe52487ab9a3fdd98ed49d","tid":1131720,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mj-P8Y7ry7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmj-P8Y7ry7s&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=5348aa96\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mj-P8Y7ry7s</a><br />\n<br />\n另一偉大笑匠 阮兆祥挑你機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}